      "content": "hey, i'm working on a new global campaign for a high-end luxury watch brand—think something in the league of Patek Philippe. i need to build out a really detailed persona for our \"ideal\" customer so our creative team can nail the visual direction. \n\ncan you give me a breakdown of the ideal consumer? i need stuff like their lifestyle, typical hobbies, where they travel, and also their general ethnicity and cultural background to make sure the branding feels authentic and \"prestige.\"",
